    "headline": "3 Insurance Stocks We Steer Clear Of",
    "summary": "Insurance firms play a critical role in the financial system, offering everything from property coverage to life insurance and specialized risk solutions. But worries about an economic slowdown and potential claims deterioration have kept sentiment in check, and over the past six months, the industry has tumbled by 3.7%. This drop was worse than the S&P 500’s 2.1% loss.",
